{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-fill-in-the-blank-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-understanding-questions-and-answers/task-8","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"title":"Vežba 8","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Naučio si da ga pokrećeš koristeći <ruby>我是<rp>(</rp><rt>wǒ shì</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby> + država. Takođe si naučio da koristiš <ruby>你<rp>(</rp><rt>nǐ</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby> da se referiš na nekoga s kim razgovaraš.</p>\n<p>Dakle, ako želite da razgovarate o državljanstvu osobe sa kojom razgovarate, koju strukturu bi trebalo da koristite?</p>\n</section>","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Slušajte zvuk i dovršite sledeću rečenicu.</p>\n</section>","explanation":"<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p><ruby>你是<rp>(</rp><rt>nǐ shì</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby> znači \"ti si\". Možete koristiti strukturu <ruby>你是<rp>(</rp><rt>nǐ shì</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby> + utaifa da razgovarate o nacionalnosti osobe sa kojom razgovarate. Na primer:</p>\n<p><ruby>你是美国人吗<rp>(</rp><rt>nǐ shì měi guó rén ma</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>？ – Jesi li Amerikanac?</p>\n<p>Takođe, možete koristiti <ruby>你是<rp>(</rp><rt>nǐ shì</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby> + ime ili profesiju da govorite o imenu ili profesiji druge osobe. Primjeri:</p>\n<p><ruby>你是刘明吗<rp>(</rp><rt>nǐ shì liú míng ma</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>？ – Jesi li ti Liu Ming?</p>\n<p><ruby>你是开发者吗<rp>(</rp><rt>nǐ shì kāi fā zhě ma</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>？ – Jesi li programer?</p>\n</section>","challengeType":22,"helpCategory":"Chinese Curriculum","superBlock":"a1-professional-chinese","block":"zh-a1-learn-understanding-questions-and-answers","lang":"zh-CN","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-understanding-questions-and-answers/task-8"},"fillInTheBlank":{"sentence":"<p>BLANK <ruby>中国人吗<rp>(</rp><rt>zhōng guó rén ma</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>？</p>","blanks":[{"answer":"你是 (nǐ shì)","feedback":"<p>Ovo znači \"ti si\".</p>"}]},"inputType":"pinyin-to-hanzi","tests":[],"transcript":null,"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company1-breakroom.png","characters":[{"character":"Wang Hua","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.4},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"ZH_A1_greetings_and_introductions_dialogue.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":8.37,"finishTimestamp":9.73},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Wang Hua","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Wang Hua","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":2.36,"dialogue":{"text":"<ruby>你是中国人吗<rp>(</rp><rt>nǐ shì zhōng guó rén ma</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>？","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Wang Hua","position":null,"opacity":0,"startTime":2.86,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null}]},"translationPending":false}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/#zh-a1-learn-understanding-questions-and-answers","dashedName":"task-8","certification":"a1-professional-chinese","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a1-professional-chinese","chapter":"zh-a1-chapter-greetings-and-introductions","module":"zh-a1-module-asking-and-giving-basic-information","block":"zh-a1-learn-understanding-questions-and-answers","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-understanding-questions-and-answers/task-9","prevChallengePath":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-understanding-questions-and-answers/task-7","id":"6911a114c5048d31545e22f2","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":19,"challengeFiles":[]}},"id":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-understanding-questions-and-answers/task-8"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}